{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"msg_YvvxVveVDvH5Z6WPlxMBiXpU","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## Plan Stage Complete for TST-001\n\n### Summary\n\n| Artifact | Location | Status |\n|----------|----------|--------|\n| Implementation Plan | `aidd/docs/plan/TST-001.md` | READY |\n| Validation Report | `aidd/docs/plan/TST-001-validation.md` | WARN |\n\n### Key Plan Highlights\n\n**5 Implementation Phases:**\n1. **Backend Foundation** (Days 1-3): RBAC filter, audit table, caching\n2. **Profile Service Integration** (Days 4-5): Role resolution service\n3. **Frontend Role Sync** (Days 6-8): Zustand store extension, SSE listener\n4. **SSE Role Events** (Days 9-10): Backend endpoint for role notifications\n5. **Testing** (Days 11-12): Unit, integration, and performance tests\n\n**Technology Adaptations from Research:**\n| PRD Assumption | Research Finding | Plan Adaptation |\n|----------------|------------------|-----------------|\n| JWT claims | X-Profile-Key headers | Custom WebFlux filter |\n| Redux | Zustand | Extend Zustand store |\n| WebSocket | SSE exists | Extend SSE infrastructure |\n| Spring Security | Not in classpath | Custom WebFlux filters |\n\n### Validation WARN Items (Non-blocking)\n\n| Item | Risk | Mitigation |\n|------|------|------------|\n| Component scan config | R-007 | Add `RbacConfig` to all profile configs |\n| Profile service API | R-008 | Define contract or use local DB table |\n\n**No blockers identified.** The plan is ready for implementation.\n\n### Next Steps\n1. Address WARN items during implementation (R-007, R-008)\n2. Create detailed tasklist with `/feature-dev-aidd:tasklist-new TST-001`\n3. Proceed to implementation with `/feature-dev-aidd:implement TST-001`"}],"model":"kimi-for-coding","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":45970,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available","promp